<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.5">
<l>toṇṭar paravac cuṭarceṉ ṟaṇava</l>
<l>vaṇṭat tamaru maṭika ḷūrpōl</l>
<l>vaṇṭa lalaiyuḷ keṇṭai miḷira</l>
<l>koṇṭa latiruṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr where the east wind rushes</l>
<l>So that keṇṭai [fish] shimmer in the pond waves,</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of the god who occupied the [whole] universe,</l>
<l>When he rose, approaching the sun, as devotees praised [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
